    "rationale": "Despite multiple credibility factor gaps identified against project requirements, the assessment package is accepted for regulatory submission as a documented gap analysis. All 13 factors have been evaluated or explicitly scoped as epistemic gaps consistent with MRL 5 requirements. The Monte Carlo UQ framework partially addresses input uncertainty. Acceptance is conditional on gap closure prior to final device submission; this package documents the current state against project requirements as required by the ASME V&V 40 framework.",
